ariba.ui.meta.persistence
Interface ObjectContext.EntityQueryFilterProvider

Enclosing class:
ObjectContext
public static interface ObjectContext.EntityQueryFilterProvider

Implement this interface if you want to add additional filtering on queries linked to an entity.

The implemented class should be registered on the ObjectContext using ObjectContext.registerQueryFilterProviderForEntityClass(String, EntityQueryFilterProvider)
